    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it shows its age both inside and out. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some clear coat fading on the roof and trunk. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some minor staining, though all essential electronics and controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs well for its mileage, but a prospective buyer should expect upcoming maintenance needs typical for a car of this vintage.",
      "price": 22500.0,
